entries.femaleVariant: V, baby, listen, got a yarn for ya... Quick biz, that is. Ya interested?
entries.maleVariant: V, dawg, listen, got a yarn for ya... Quick biz, that is. Ya interested?

entries.femaleVariant: Indeed.
All right. Lay it on me.
Was cruisin' the net, ya feel? An' I spotted an interestin' classified.
Now, I'm a serious man, V. And serious matters are what, if not all, that concern me.
Can do. Will do.
Gonna give it a think.
Can't you get it?
OK. Will do.
Zippin' ya the detes on the seller. And luck be with ya all the way.
Sendin' me out to do your shopping? Want a case of Nicola with that? Algae chips?
entries.maleVariant: Sendin' me out to do your shoppin'? Want a case of Nicola with that? Algae chips?

entries.femaleVariant: Think on it, V. A treasure, and someone's willin' to part with it. Now, who does that?
That's my girl.
Somebody's sellin' a book of spells. Edition datin' from before the first Net crash.
Not just yet.
Sometime, maybe. Not now.
A'ight. Ain't no fire burnin'.
So, gonna gimme a listen, lend little Nix an ear?
Wait. Lemme guess. Performance enhancers? A used Mr. Stud, cheap?
Now, you know a thing or two 'bout that, don't ya? Like how much that soft could run ya and earn ya.
Might not mean much to you, but it sounds like a treasure to a netrunner. Fuckin' Dead-Sea-Scroll yummy.
Want me to klep it for you, don't you.
entries.maleVariant: Want me to klep it for you, don't ya?

entries.femaleVariant: Uh-uh, no kleppin' required. Just buy the damn thing. Reimburse ya twofold.
Aaand? Ya thunk on it yet?
The hard up, V. And desperados got this... unsavory side. They're unpredictable. One word off their mood... an' they reach for their heat.
That's why I need you to meet the seller. You got heat at the ready.
Gotta give it a think.
Don't rightly see what there is to ruminate on, but you do you. Just don't make me wait if there ain't no need, huh?
